des:
Use Alexa to control your Bharat Switch devices! After connecting Alexa to your devices in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our “Bharat Switch” app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in “Bharat Switch” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Android, IOS or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search “Bharat Switch” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable “Bharat Switch” skill, and you'll be navigated to “Bharat Switch” login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the switch.”
“Alexa, turn off the plug.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
